docs.text: Pinry ¶ The open-source core of Pinry, a tiling image board system for people who want to save, tag, and share images, videos and webpages in an easy to skim through format. As Seen On ¶

docs.text: Docs ¶ Timestrap's docs are built with mkdocs . If you have dev dependencies installed, pipenv install --dev , then you can use the following commands: gulp docs:serve for testing gulp docs:build to build the files gulp docs:publish to publish to github
